{"tid":1967234,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人大左，越來越懷念以前","createTime":"2020-04-10T18:31:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T06:49:40.000Z","uid":183576,"like":63,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"b8777a23857417feb3fde3274217fd280d19ca04","tid":1967234,"uid":183576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T18:31:40.000Z","msg":"身邊一切都變得好陌生<br />\n阿婆已經唔再同我地一齊住，冇人再日日買零食同早餐比我地食<br />\n我亦都唔會再為食到果汁糖、白糖糕而開心興奮<br />\n以前儲錢買一隻witcher3就夠我開心好耐，依家儲錢買樓只令我苦惱<br />\n以往好愛呢個街區，依家因福建幫而痛恨<br />\n人變得越來越複雜，已經唔期盼中學同學嘅純真友誼，只希望同事唔好害我<br />\n曾經有純粹嘅愛情，對方會只因為我係我而愛，而依家無論付出幾多，都係幻影<br />\n連網友都變左，知更鳥、LoraineC、多啲A夢只能永遠留喺2019嘅連登陪連豬連狗一齊玩<br />\n香港千瘡百孔，細個千禧慶典嘅和平快樂同義士一樣冇可能再返來<br />\n<br />\n點解一切都唔同左<br />\n童年嘅世界冇咁苦澀 點樣先返到去<br />\n<br />\n我地最終到底會喺追逐中終老先 定係喺追憶中失速先"},{"pid":"82f2d8e27d59a37e263ae61a6c2f815526e7f2af","tid":1967234,"uid":84596,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T18:33:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8ddf5c45abddaf2147e0300e60faf75e2677c6f","tid":1967234,"uid":346370,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T18:36:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />時間過左去冇得返轉頭真係唏噓"},{"pid":"6198255534cf348e1ef31db3a3aee6bdee595d34","tid":1967234,"uid":183576,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T18:36:14.000Z","msg":"深夜有感<br />\n人生呢條單行道真係好難行<br />\n<br />\n喺呢個亂世中 連甜蜜都係一種奢侈<br />\n我地到底要如何上路<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日買左一盒細個鍾意嘅嘉雲糖，邊食邊喊好似個傻仔咁，我依家可以食成盒都冇人鬧我了，但果種快樂一啲都搵唔到返來了"},{"pid":"4ff042de3a7ef02840df32007be1477861f72739","tid":1967234,"uid":183576,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T18:40:30.000Z","msg":"D'Yquem好珍貴 好香甜<br />\n<br />\n但果種幸福感完全比唔上細個偷飲嘅果汁 甚至不如高中開P飲嘅apple cider<br />\n<br />\n長大會得到好多野 但失去左更多"},{"pid":"370a8b9792f967afd0f57c5817cbb77860ba0277","tid":1967234,"uid":183576,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f8ddf5c45abddaf2147e0300e60faf75e2677c6f","tid":1967234,"uid":346370,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T18:36:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />時間過左去冇得返轉頭真係唏噓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T18:41:26.000Z","msg":"今日路過超市興起買左盒糖，點知一食就滿心酸苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4834581b4f82cb15e8f48fccf6de75aa624d557","tid":1967234,"uid":183576,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T18:47:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n盒糖明明一樣 點解感受唔同曬"},{"pid":"79c67e91083053ab86c9f6155e899fb2aeba441e","tid":1967234,"uid":54528,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T18:49:33.000Z","msg":"我要打打打多支botox"},{"pid":"616eada7e75355f6b5d30107723e4b162e256b05","tid":1967234,"uid":145923,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T18:49:37.000Z","msg":"有過已經係最好，最悲哀既係，從來都沒有。"},{"pid":"8bf1abc15575666d0f3b63a8458f14187008b48f","tid":1967234,"uid":183576,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"616eada7e75355f6b5d30107723e4b162e256b05","tid":1967234,"uid":145923,"like":2,"dislik